<task><p>Which method(s) work on any quadratic equation?</p></task>

<task><p>Which method is fastest if one side of the equation is a perfect square?</p></task>

<task><p>For each equation, name the easiest method for solving, then solve.<ol>
  <li><p><m>x^2-7=0</m></p></li>
  <li><p><m>x^2=7x</m></p></li>
  <li><p><m>x^2-7x=8</m></p></li>
  <li><p><m>(x-7)^2=8</m></p></li>
  <li><p><m>x^2=7x-8</m></p></li>
  <li><p><m>x^2-8x=4</m></p></li></ol></p></task>
